import React from "react";
import Dropdown from 'react-multilevel-dropdown';
import 'react-dropdown/style.css';



const CategoryDropdown = () => {
  
return <Dropdown
  title='Dropdown title'
>
  <Dropdown.Item
    onClick={() => {}}
  >
    Item 1
  </Dropdown.Item>
  <Dropdown.Item>
    Item 2
    <Dropdown.Submenu position='right'>
      <Dropdown.Item>
        Subitem 1
      </Dropdown.Item>
      <Dropdown.Item>
        Subitem 2
      </Dropdown.Item>
    </Dropdown.Submenu>
  </Dropdown.Item>
  <Dropdown.Item>
    Item 3
  </Dropdown.Item>
</Dropdown>};
export default CategoryDropdown;
